se.opendataexchange.ethernetip4j.services
Class UnconnectedMessageManagerRequest

java.lang.Object
  se.opendataexchange.ethernetip4j.services.UnconnectedMessageManagerRequest

public class UnconnectedMessageManagerRequest
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used for creating read- and write CIP requests for ControlLogix communication. The "Logix5000 Data Access" and the TCP/IP specification have been used to determine the packet structures.

Byte Segment Type
0-23 Header EthernetIpEncapsulationHeader
24-35 Command specific data EthernetIpCommandSpecificData
36-39 Data item EthernetIpItemStruct
40-45 CIP packet request CipPacketRequest
46-53 CIP command specific data request CipCommandSpecificDataRequest
